public class FlowSession { public static final FlowSession NULL = new FlowSession(); protected CascadingServices cascadingServices; private FlowProcess currentProcess = FlowProcess.NULL; public FlowSession() { } public FlowSession( CascadingServices cascadingServices ) { this.cascadingServices = cascadingServices; } public void setCurrentProcess( FlowProcess currentProcess ) { this.currentProcess = currentProcess; } public FlowProcess getCurrentProcess() { return currentProcess; } public CascadingServices getCascadingServices() { return cascadingServices; } public String getID() { return currentProcess.getStringProperty( Flow.CASCADING_FLOW_ID ); } }